column5: Jefit Beginner Home Routine for Male
column9: Jefit Built-in Bulking Routine For Beginners. This routine was designed for bodybuilding beginners who want to gain muscle. This 4 day split routine consists of chest,shoulders,back,arms and legs training. The goal of this routine is to gain maximum amount of muscle while keeping fat gain at minimum.
